videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu becomes the first Division I player to tally 2,000 points, 1,000 assists and 1,000 rebounds in a career.

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu says getting to 1,000 rebounds was for Kobe Bryant and to be able to do it on 2/24 is special.

videos.description: After Sabrina Ionescu makes college basketball history, her Oregon teammates spray her with water.
